"If you modify your configuration files, you will need to re-verify and re-"
"cache your configuration files before restarting Nagios. If you don't re-"
"generate the precached object file, Nagios will continue to use your old "
"configuration because it is now reading from the precached file, rather than "
"your source configuration files."
msgstr ""

